snippet.title: Binary Numbers -  Math Bites with Danica McKellar
snippet.description:
Join host Danica McKellar as she demystifies the 1s and 0s of binary numbers. Welcome to Math Bites! New episodes every Thursday.

Subscribe for Math Bites: http://bit.ly/Sub2Nerdist

Follow Danica on Twitter: https://twitter.com/danicamckellar
Check her out on the web: http://www.danicamckellar.com/
Get her math books:
http://www.mathdoesntsuck.com/
http://www.kissmymath.com/

Follow Nerdist on Twitter: https://twitter.com/NerdistDotCom
Check out Nerdist.com: http://www.nerdist.com

Cast:
Danica McKellar -- host
David Eckstein -- himself
Ashley Eckstein -- David's stalker
Jonathan Bennett -- creepy guy
 
Jen Drohan & John Highsmith -- kissing couple
Brian Clarke -- puppeteer for Talk Show Host
Danica McKellar, Cara Santa Maria, Kristen Rutherford -- The Andrew Sisters
Benji Schwimmer & Torri Smith -- Swing Dancers
Brian Cohen -- man in bathtub, man holding pink dog
Nick Nicotera -- man on laptop, man holding blue dog
Meghan Hooper White -- Sparkly Disco Singer
Karen Prell & John Tartaglia - Puppeteers
Mike Dirolf -- computer science consultant
